cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the SSB block power to an excessively high value of 100 dBm will exceed regulatory limits and cause synchronization signal transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 區塊功率設定為過高的值 100 dBm，將超過法規限制，並導致同步信號傳輸失敗。
